d affiliate links to help you discover quality nail care and beauty products.\n      </p>\n      <p className=\"mb-4\">\n        While we strive to provide accurate product information, prices, descriptions, and availability \n        are subject to change by the third-party retailers. We are not responsible for pricing errors, \n        product availability, shipping delays, product quality, or fulfillment issues. All purchases are \n        made directly through third-party retailers, and their terms, conditions, return policies, and \n        privacy practices apply to your transaction.\n      </p>\n      <p className=\"mb-4\">\n        Our website may contain links to external third-party websites. Mirelle Inspo is not responsible \n        for the content, accuracy, privacy practices, or policies of these external sites. We encourage \n        you to review the terms and privacy policies of any third-party sites you visit.\n      </p>\n\n      <h2 className=\"text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2\">6. Content Accuracy & Disclaimers</h2>\n      <p className=\"mb-4\">\n        The information provided on Mirelle Inspo is for educational, inspirational, and entertainment \n        purposes only. Our blog content about nail care, nail ideas, seasonal looks, and beauty tips \n        represents our personal opinions, experiences, and research.\n      </p>\n      <p className=\"mb-4\">\n        <strong>Not Professional Advice:</strong> Content on our website does not constitute professional \n        medical, dermatological, health, or beauty advice. Always consult with qualified professionals \n        before trying new nail care treatments, using products if you have allergies or sensitivities, \n        or addressing any nail or skin health concerns.\n      </p>\n      <p className=\"mb-4\">\n        <strong>Individual Results May Vary:</strong> Results from products, techniques, or recommendations \n        featured on our website may vary based on individual factors. We cannot guarantee specific outcomes \n        or results.\n      </p>\n\n      <h2 className=\"text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2\">7. User-Generated Content</h2>\n      <p className=\"mb-4\">\n        If you submit comments, reviews, feedback, suggestions, or other content to our website (via \n        comments, contact forms, or social media), you grant Mirelle Inspo a non-exclusive, royalty-free, \n        perpetual, worldwide license to use, reproduce, modify, adapt, publish, and display such content \n        in connection with our services. You represent that you own or have the necessary rights to submit \n        such content.\n      </p>\n\n      <h2 className=\"text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2\">8. Advertising & Analytics</h2>\n      <p className=\"mb-4\">\n        Mirelle Inspo uses third-party advertising networks (including Google AdSense) and analytics services \n        to display ads and analyze website traffic. These services may use cookies and similar technologies \n        to collect information about your browsing behavior. For more details, please review our Privacy Policy.\n      </p>\n\n      <h2 className=\"text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2\">9. Limitation of Liability</h2>\n      <p className=\"mb-4\">\n        To the fullest extent permitted by law, Mirelle Inspo and its owners, contributors, and affiliates \n        shall not be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, consequential, or punitive damages arising \n        from: your use of the website; errors, omissions, or inaccuracies in content; loss of data, profits, \n        or business opportunities; personal injury or property damage related to website use; issues arising \n        from products purchased through affiliate links; or unauthorized access to your data.\n      </p>\n      <p className=\"mb-4\">\n        <strong>Use at Your Own Risk:</strong> Your use of Mirelle Inspo is at your sole risk. The website \n        and all content are provided on an \"AS IS\" and \"AS AVAILABLE\" basis without warranties of any kind, \n        either express or implied.\n      </p>\n\n      <h2 className=\"text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2\">10. Indemnification</h2>\n      <p className=\"mb-4\">\n        You agree to indemnify, defend, and hold harmless Mirelle Inspo, its owners, employees, and affiliates \n        from any claims, damages, losses, liabilities, and expenses (including reasonable legal fees) arising \n        from: your use of the website; your violation of these Terms & Conditions; your violation of any \n        third-party rights; or any content you submit to our website.\n      </p>\n\n      <h2 className=\"text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2\">11. Copyright Infringement Claims</h2>\n      <p className=\"mb-4\">\n        We respect intellectual property rights. If you believe content on our website infringes your copyright, \n        please contact us at team.mirelle@gmail.com with: identification of the copyrighted work; URL or \n        location of the allegedly infringing material; your contact information; a statement of good faith \n        belief that use is unauthorized; and a statement of accuracy under penalty of perjury.\n      </p>\n\n      <h2 className=\"text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2\">12. Governing Law & Dispute Resolution</h2>\n      <p className=\"mb-4\">\n        These Terms & Conditions shall be governed by and construed in accordance with applicable laws. \n        Any disputes arising from these terms or your use of the website shall be resolved through binding \n        arbitration or in the courts of appropriate jurisdiction.\n      </p>\n\n      <h2 className=\"text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2\">13. Changes to Terms</h2>\n      <p className=\"mb-4\">\n        We reserve the right to modify or update these Terms & Conditions at any time without prior notice. \n        Changes will be effective immediately upon posting on this page with a revised \"Last Updated\" date. \n        Your continued use of the website after changes are posted constitutes acceptance of the modified terms.\n      </p>\n\n      <h2 className=\"text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2\">14. Severability</h2>\n      <p className=\"mb-4\">\n        If any provision of these Terms & Conditions is found to be invalid or unenforceable, the remaining \n        provisions shall continue in full force and effect.\n      </p>\n\n      <h2 className=\"text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2\">15. Contact Us</h2>\n      <p className=\"mb-4\">\n        For questions, concerns, or requests regarding these Terms & Conditions, please contact us at:{\" \"}\n        <a href=\"mailto:team.mirelle@gmail.com\" className=\"text-blue-600 underline hover:text-blue-800\">\n          team.mirelle@gmail.com\n        </a>\n      </p>\n\n      <p className=\"mt-8 text-sm text-gray-500 italic\">Last Updated: October 6, 2025</p>\n    </div>\n  );\n}\n"
